{
  "stem": "22237.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I sat on the bench, and I remember looking at these nice houses, but the sky was red from all the fires, from all the synagogues that were burning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saw opposite in the house, there was-- windows were broken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a woman walking back and forth with a little child on her shoulder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was dark, but you could see her trying to kind of put that child-- that baby to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and then-- and then I was looking down on the bench where I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In big letter it said, Juden verboten.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews are not permitted to sit here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, well, I can't push my luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have to get up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody is going to find me on that bench.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I kept on running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But while sitting on the bench, I decided to-- I had a little money from the things, I thought, I decided to run to the railway station because my sister-- my second sister Mary was still in Munich.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I thought I'll go to Munich because this way I'll go away from here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- and while-- while running, I saw so many men being pulled out of the houses, and children crying.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[GERMAN], you know, send my-- give me my, my, my-- give me my father back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And women crying at the windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I run all along this street, Kaiserstrasse, that leads to the-- to the German railway station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And even there, Jews still had offices there, and some of them were trying to hide in their offices.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that didn't help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were-- I saw them just running along.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I saw-- by that time it was getting a little bit lighter already.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
